information = Aethur Moltenbeard was the respected and beloved king of Loch Modar. Known for his unyielding sense of justice and commitment to his people, he led with honor and strength. His reign was marked by peace and prosperity until his untimely assassination. His successor was his son Zarnaldis Moltenbeard.
notes = Aethur's legacy lives on in the hearts of his people and in the actions of those who seek to bring his assassin to justice. He was a paragon of dwarven nobility and valor, embodying the highest ideals of his culture.

