Abilities[dnd-list]=;-Divine Smite: Aethur can expend a spell slot to deal radiant damage to a target in addition to his weapon's damage.;-Lay on Hands: Aethur can heal a total of 100 hit points, divided as he sees fit among creatures he touches.;-Aura of Protection: Aethur and friendly creatures within 10 feet of him gain a +5 bonus to all saving throws.;-Sacred Weapon: Aethur can imbue one weapon that he is holding with positive energy, adding +5 to attack rolls made with that weapon.;-Turn the Unholy: As an action, Aethur can present his holy symbol and speak a prayer censuring fiends and undead. Each fiend or undead that can see or hear him within 30 feet must make a Wisdom saving throw.;-Divine Health: Aethur is immune to disease.;-Purity of Spirit: Aethur is always under the effects of a *Protection from Evil and Good* spell.;-Holy Nimbus: Aethur can use his action to cause an aura of sunlight to radiate from him. This aura lasts for 1 minute or until he dismisses it as a bonus action. He emits bright light in a 30-foot radius and dim light 30 feet beyond that. His enemies in the bright light take 10 radiant damage.;-Commanding Presence: Aethur can use his action to inspire fear and respect in his enemies. Each creature within 60 feet of him that can see or hear him must make a Wisdom saving throw or be frightened for 1 minute.
